name: Chrysis Chrysoviolacea
description:
Augmented Reality Digital Sculpture of Glitched Insect Wrapped in Analog Video Feedback Textures. 

"Chrysis Chrysoviolacea" is the first release of "Insecta Teknika" - a three part mini-series by Micah Alhadeff and CIPOTE
